{"tid":834391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【支聞】黑龍江17歲少年沉迷鹹網 強姦69歲老人","createTime":"2018-09-24T07:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T03:17:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e2864db32fca3b0e7d0dce16771306d83e90a4","tid":834391,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1876400/org/5a055f66e7180b81a94586b2f2b36c12.jpg/y0z2JF4LTGYFCuZFZrDltO1DmSlxGHgxjuDZ047g2dM?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1876400%2Forg%2F5a055f66e7180b81a94586b2f2b36c12.jpg%2Fy0z2JF4LTGYFCuZFZrDltO1DmSlxGHgxjuDZ047g2dM%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=5d856e74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n17歲未成年犯郭強在網路上流覽了大量色情視頻，一次他到同學親戚家吃飯，抑制不住自己的慾望，強姦了同學69歲的親戚。<br />\n<br />\n報道又提到，管教所是省內未成年犯的刑罰執行機關，同時亦是教育部門批准的哈爾濱市第150中學。未成年犯會在管教所內服刑，過着有規律的學習和生活。他們除了會參加職業技能導向的勞動工作，還會有初中程度的課堂，甚至有法制講堂、孔子學堂等，目的就是要補足他們所缺失的家庭、社會教育，以養成規範的行為修養。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/236863/%E5%85%A7%E5%AA%92%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9%E9%BB%91%E9%BE%8D%E6%B1%9F%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E7%8A%AF%E7%AE%A1%E6%95%99%E6%89%80-%E6%9C%8917%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E6%B2%89%E8%BF%B7%E9%B9%B9%E7%B6%B2%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A669%E6%AD%B2%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%2F236863%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AA%2592%25E4%25BB%258B%25E7%25B4%25B9%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%25BE%258D%25E6%25B1%259F%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%258A%25AF%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%2589%2580-%25E6%259C%258917%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25B2%2589%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E9%25B9%25B9%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A7%25A669%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E8%2580%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=I351fSihAHQRxhP70sHOzIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e670b4c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.